@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_bnneti(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.cos(wp.abs((v0 + 0.50 * v1 + 0.65)))
    v0 = ((wp.sin(v2 + 0.27) + 0.03) - v0)
    tmp = (((tmp + 0.67 * tmp + 0.86) / wp.abs(v0 + 0.25)) * v0)
    v0 = v0
    data[tid] = v0
